      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<h3>SINGING A VERSE</h3><p>When you sing a <strong>verse</strong>, you combine a <strong>volume</strong>, a <strong>key </strong>and a <strong>tone </strong>you learned. These three aspects determine the <strong>verse</strong>’s MP cost, targets and effect.</p><p>The <strong>volume </strong>determines the sound intensity of your <strong>verse </strong>(and the creatures you can reach with it).</p><ul><li>Each <strong>tone </strong>determines the general effects of your <strong>verse</strong>. (see @UUID[.mm3q742jIIhvWG1U]{Tone List})</li><li>Each <strong>key</strong> has an associated damage type, status effect, Attribute, and recovery. These modify the effects determined by the tone of your verse. (see @UUID[.W4kQjYXrLRVomFdg]{Key List})</li></ul><blockquote><p><em><strong>Example:</strong> you might combine a <strong>low volume </strong>with the <strong>key of Flame </strong>and a <strong>haunting tone </strong>to inflict <strong>shaken </strong>on a single creature for 10 Mind Points, or you could combine a <strong>medium volume </strong>with the <strong>key of Iron </strong>and an <strong>energetic tone </strong>to allow your allies to make additional progress on Clocks when using <strong>Willpower</strong>.</em></p></blockquote><p></p><table style=\"width:96.8701%;height:68px;border:1px solid black\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:12.2257%\"></col><col style=\"width:4.85893%\"></col><col style=\"width:82.9154%\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>Volume</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center;height:17px\"><strong>MP</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px\"> <strong>Targets</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>Low</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center;height:17px\"><strong>10</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px\"> <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Yourself </span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">or </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">another creature you can see who can hear you.</span> </td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>Medium</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center;height:17px\"><strong>20</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px\"> <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Every ally who can hear you.</span> </td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>High</strong></td><td style=\"text-align:center;height:17px\"><strong>30</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px\"> <span class=\"fontstyle0\">Every enemy who can hear you.</span> </td></tr></tbody></table><p> </p><table style=\"width:96.5571%;height:153px;border:1px solid black\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:14.4231%\"></col><col style=\"width:16.8269%\"></col><col style=\"width:21.7949%\"></col><col style=\"width:21.9551%\"></col><col style=\"width:25.1603%\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>Key</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Type</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Status Effect</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Attribute</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Recovery</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:left\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.cmo71xT0QgJCOOMp]{Flame}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Fire</strong> @ICON[fire]</span></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Shaken</strong> </td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Might</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Hit Points</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.QZOttsghYTCeqnCx]{Frost}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Ice</strong> @ICON[ice]</span></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Weak</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Willpower</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Mind Points</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.qpRWVxEuy6iHiUCP]{Iron}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>Physical</strong> @ICON[physical]</span></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Slow</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Willpower</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Mind Points</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.ymWN6HhIvwji1Y39]{Radiance}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Light</strong> @ICON[light]</td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Dazed</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Insight</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Hit Points</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.zzyNprcgb1RF2niW]{Shadow}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Dark</strong> @ICON[dark]</td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Weak</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Dexterity</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Mind Points</strong></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.dyyFIR6iB0brrh1I]{Stone}</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Earth</strong> @ICON[earth]</td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Dazed</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Might</strong></td><td style=\"height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Hit Points</strong><