    {
      "sort": 300000,
      "name": "TONE LIST",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "mm3q742jIIhvWG1U",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>CALM TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.XCtijox9eBrBNSno]{Calm Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each target recovers <strong>【key recovery】</strong> equal to <strong>【10 + twice your current Willpower die size】</strong>. This amount increases by 10 if you are level <strong>20 or higher</strong>, or by 20 if you are level 40 or higher.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>ENERGETIC TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.XvkMOHPXUg0ikDkf]{Energetic Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Until the start of your next turn, when a target succeeds on a Check that includes <strong>【key Attribute】</strong> and that Check allows them to advance or turn back a Clock, they may fill or erase an additional section of that Clock.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>FRANTIC TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.mtKts9zjHlweSVk4]{Frantic Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each target suffers <strong>【key type】</strong> damage equal to <strong>twice</strong> your current <strong>Willpower</strong> die size. This tone deals 10 extra damage if you are level 20 or higher, or 20 extra damage if you are level 40 or higher.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>HAUNTING TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.CynydNkxJS1HZVlJ]{Haunting Tune}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each target suffers <strong>【key status effect】</strong>. Each target also loses Resistance to <strong>【key type】</strong> damage (if they have it) until the start of your next turn.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>LIVELY TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.zLxqETSi6zbRkWKu]{Lively Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each target treats their <strong>【key Attribute】</strong> as being one die size higher (up to a maximum of <strong>【d12】</strong>) until the start of your next turn.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>MENACING TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.8QMh3jUtgmIMy9Jb]{Menacing Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>The first time each target suffers damage before the start of your next turn, that damage becomes <strong>【key type】</strong>. This can trigger once for each target of the verse, separately.</p><table style=\"width:100%;height:34px;border:1px solid black\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>SOLEMN TONE</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px\"><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.yidpNKJQMA7dSBsc]{Solemn Tone}</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Each target recovers from <strong>【key status effect】</strong>. Each target also gains Resistance to <strong>【key type】</strong> damage until the start of your next turn.</p>",
        "markdown": ""
      },
