      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<ol><li><p>To <strong>automate</strong> class feature, add the following item to your character sheet: @UUID[Compendium.projectfu.skills.Item.nu7QnUu7tmVv6zxU]{Verse}</p></li><li><p>A full list of <strong>keys</strong> and <strong>tones</strong> can be found here: @UUID[.W4kQjYXrLRVomFdg]{KEY LIST} and @UUID[.mm3q742jIIhvWG1U]{TONE LIST}.</p></li><li><p>Open the verse sheet and navigate to \"<strong>Details</strong>\" tab</p></li><li><p>There are two dropdowns, select a key followed by a tone.</p></li><li><p>To <strong>start singing</strong>, roll the Verse feature and combine a key, tone and volume in the dialog menu.</p></li></ol>"
      },
